# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).


## [15.0.1.0.2] - 2024/07/05
### Improved
- Smaller font
- Use S/O# in the last line of the template


## [15.0.1.0.1] - 2024/06/24
### Changed
- Smaller S/O line padding in PDF template


## [15.0.1.0] - 2024/06/14
### Changed
- Update invoice PDF template
- Update P/O PDF template
- Update S/O PDF template


## [15.0.0.1.11] - 2024/05/29
### Changed
- Change report format of sale order, purchase order and invoice


## [15.0.0.1.10] - 2024/04/26
